<subSubSection id="1CDF5F80FFAFFFF56DC2FAEEFCF8AEA4" pageId="11" pageNumber="1524" type="description">
<paragraph id="547A0C0BFFAFFFF56DC2FAEEFCF8AEA4" blockId="11.[178,1084,1395,1446]" pageId="11" pageNumber="1524">Variation: Size: length 6.0-7.0 mm; width 1.5-2.0 mm. The elytra may be entirely black, or flavotestaceous in elytral basal half and black in remainder.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
